node.text:
When painting a beehive there are a few things you should keep in mind. 
🐝Paint with none-toxic, latex paint with low VOCs
🐝 it is said that a bee’s favorite colors are violet, purple and blue
🐝 don’t paint on the inside or walkways of the beehive
🌻 Check out this video for more beehive painting tips and bee facts!
🍯 if you are interested in beekeeping yourself there are a few spots open in the beekeeping club that I’ve joined! Check it out at @sarvodayafarms

To my Beautiful Birthday Puffy Princess! 💕✨ You are the absolute light of my life and I love every single second with you! 
To us ✨🥂✨

node.text:
Happy Birthday to my most special clone! Kylie, you have the most empathetic and caring heart. Knowing you and having the connection we do has been such a beautiful gift. I can’t wait to grow old together, to sit on our front porch and to look into each others wrinkly faces and still crack up just as hard. You make the world such a beautiful place to be. You quite literally feed my soul. To try to put the way I love you into words would just be an injustice to it so with all of the emphasis that this little keyboard phone will allow I LOVE THE HECK OUT OF YOU!!! 
To us ✨🥂✨

node.text:
Almost another year has gone by and I have to say that I have never felt more myself than I do now. Life has given me many insane experiences and I am thankful for each and every one. I especially am grateful for what challenges this life has thrown my way because without an occasional rumble I would never have learned the unstoppable motivation I feel while building myself back up and the beauty of my strong family and meaningful friendships.
There have been many birthdays where I look at my future and question if I am ready for it. But today I am looking forward and instead saying, “Are you ready for me? Because I’m ready for you… so bring it on sucker!” 😜
